Class PopulatedFields<E extends Enum<E> & FieldType,T extends FieldContainer>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mpxj.common.PopulatedFields<E,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - field enumeration
    T - object type

    public class PopulatedFields<E extends Enum<E> & FieldType,T extends FieldContainer>
extends Object
    Given a collection of objects containing fields, return a set representing all of the fields which have a non-null value in any of the objects.
